    <h3>One Extra Project...</h3>
    <p>There's only one project you won't find on the "classes" page, this one! You'll find the technical details on the side.</p>
    <p>I had originally created a static page for my portfolio, but found that it was really complicated to go in and edit the html for
    every single project I'd created, so instead I spent a ton of time making this dynamic website. It still has a lot of kinks to work out,
    but I'm really proud of the end result!</p>
    <p>This site is still a work in progress, so expect a lot of changes. The next item on my list is finishing the resume page, hopefully that'll be done soon!</p>
